{
  "name": "HeaderFooter",
  "summary": "<p>不能将 <strong>HeaderFooter</strong> 对象添加到 <strong>HeadersFooters</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>PageSetup</strong> 对象的 <strong>DifferentFirstPageHeaderFooter</strong> 属性可指定不同的首页。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表页面左对齐的页眉内容为“Test”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftHeader</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 页脚中居中对齐的图片对比度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CenterFooter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Picture</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单一页眉或页脚。<strong>HeaderFooter</strong> 对象是 <strong>HeadersFooters</strong> 集合的一个成员。<strong>HeadersFooters</strong> 集合包含指定工作簿节中的所有页眉和页脚。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Picture",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>PictureFormat</strong> 对象，该对象代表指定页眉或页脚中包含的图片字段。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示工作表 Sheet1 页眉中左对齐的图片亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftHeader</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Picture</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表页面页脚右对齐的图片颜色转换设置为灰度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightFooter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Picture</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureGrayscale\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Graphic",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Text",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Text</strong> 对象，该对象代表指定页眉或页脚中包含的文本。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表页面左对齐的页眉内容为“Hello”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LeftHeader</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Hello&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 页面居中对齐的页脚内容。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PageSetup</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pages</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CenterFooter</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}